Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:16.23,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰も彼もが{\fscx85}Rival{\fscx100} 混沌の{\fscx85}Desire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:20.71,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscx75\blur3}Hide and seek so dangerous night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.57,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Tick tick tack 時計仕掛け above the 摩天楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.61,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}そっと忍ばす {\fscx75}My heart is a trap and bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:32.91,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}Ah-ah-ah 群がる視線を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:33.95,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Who's the survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.17,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}勝負は一度きり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.27,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今 火を点けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:46.73,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ジリジリと 求めるGimme more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.71,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}誰かに盗られる前に ほら {\fscx75}Love is burning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.97,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}熱を感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.15,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}ヒリヒリと {\fscx100}刺激的{\fscx75}Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.15,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 150)\blur3\fs30\fsp-3}Feel it now, feel it now, feel it now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:02.29,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導火線の行方は風まかせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.09,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運命の{\fscx75}Countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:04.11,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜風也茫然不解的旋律正在吹響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:08.61,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這既不是笑談也不是遊戲 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:16.23,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他人皆是對手 混沌的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:20.71,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}躲貓貓 如此危險的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.57,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘀嗒嘀嗒 摩天樓上時鐘作響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.61,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悄然隱匿的 我心如陷阱與炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:32.91,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊啊 脫離成群的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:33.95,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倖存者會是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.17,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勝負僅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.27,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 點燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:46.73,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多賜予
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.71,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盜走前 你看 愛在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.97,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觸到了熱氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.15,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.15,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:02.29,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導火線的行蹤就承載於風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.09,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命運的倒計時
